description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene (Lactobacillus cremoris; Lactococcus lactis subsp. cremoris; Streptococcus cremoris; Streptococcus hollandicus; Streptococcus lactis B; Streptococcus lactis subsp. cremoris.
